      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Port Louis ¶  ¶ Mauritius ¶ Municipality of Port Louis, ¶ Town Hall, ¶ 14th August ¶  ¶ 189 ¶ 6 ¶ Sir,...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">M96.08.14<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From [T]. Henri to John Clayton</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 3371, unit 637, VPRS 3181/P Town Clerk's files, VA 511 Melbourne, Public Record office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">Proofed.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Port Louis<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; font-style: italic; ">Mauritius</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; font-style: italic; ">Municipality of Port Louis,</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; font-style: italic; ">Town Hall,</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">14th August<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; font-style: italic; ">189</seg>6</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With reference to your letter of 27th June last, I have the honor, by direction of His Worship the Mayor, to acknowledge the receipt of copy of the ninth edition of "Baron Ferd. von Mueller's work on select extra tropical Plants", also of his letter to you on the subject<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to J. Clayton, 30 March 1896.</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #C00000; ">Error? 96-03-</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">20</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with memorandum of directions for sowing, and lists of desiderata from the Director of the Botanical Gardens.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I regret to have to inform you that the Eucalyptus seeds, so kindly procured by Baron von Mueller and Mr Guilfoyle, and which you advertize under separate registered covers have not been received. His Worship expects however they will reach him by next mail, and desires me in the meantime, to request that you will be good enough to tender his best thanks to his Colleague of Melbourne, to Baron von Mueller and to Mr Guilfoyle, for their very precious gifts, and that you will also be pleased to forward the enclosed letters to their respective addresses.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">The letter to M has not been found. ??</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>A MS annotation shows the enclosed letters were forwarded on 19 September 1896. On 29 October 1896 [T.] Henri wrote to J. Clayton thanking him for advising him that the enclosed letter had been forwarded to M.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">He also says that a further sending of euc. seeds obtained by the Sec. of Lands had not yet arrived.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">File reference for the 29/10/96 letter?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honour to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your very obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[T]. Henri</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Town-Clerk</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">To John Clayton Esqre</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Town-Clerk</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Town-Hall — Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Victoria — Australia</p>
         </div>
